{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, these tools are superior to other potential software tools for various reasons.",
    "For example, CiteSpaceV can be an alternative.",
    "Still, it is not that flexible and requires a lot of time to master its pretty complex user interface.",
    "At the same time, Histcite is confined to WoS and unable to interpret the Scopus dataset (Fahimnia et al. 2015), Bib Excel requires extra skill set and experience to conduct a modest analysis (Ampah et al. 2021), Pajek requires \".",
    "Net\" dataset."
  ]
}